                <h1 class="display-5">Events at The Block Co</h1>
                <P class="test">The Block co.’s event side is what I like to call ‘The Underground Restaurant experience” It goes back to a time when restaurants and bars were meant for social engagement, a time when it was all about food, fun, ease, friends and new experiences. The Block Co will host your next event by working with your budget, building menu options, and supplying all the essentials. Weather it’s a fathers birthday experience, girls night out or a small, intimate wedding celebration. The Block co can offer something truly unique. (Please keep in mind, the space is for small intimate gatherings) Contact the Block Co to book your event.</P>
                <P class="test">Follow our Instagram (@theblockco2016) and our Facebook page (@theblockcoburlington) to see when the next Block co monthly event is. Tickets will be sold in store for a maximum of 20 guests. These events are BYOB social mixers, with one of the largest charcuterie boards you will ever see and a special chef item to be announced at the event.</P>
                <P class="test">When all else fails……..cheese</P>
